 for only $139.99 on Amazon at time of review. It can last up to 11 hours on one charge, so you likely won&#39;t run out of juice in the middle of note-taking and it includes 16 GB of storage. Anyone looking for a Mac notebook should look at the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MJVM2LL-11-6-Inch-Integrated-Graphics/dp/B01425MCEA?ttr_best-laptops-for-college-students-20&amp;ascsubtag=TTRV-ttr:en_US_43_PicStory_20\">MacBook Air 11.6&#34; LED Laptop MJVM2LLA</a>.","<br/><em><br/></em>","<br/><em><br/></em>"]},"id":"41405841-0099-49ec-92aa-60f816bf213e","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Inexpensive Laptops"},"id":"8ccf9978-087b-4f8d-93fa-a0f72aa0c079","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/JpCTVkFYqW63F4fpR2pMrG.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":false,"importSrc":"http://media.bestofmicro.com/0/M/786694/original/Inexpensive-Laptop.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JpCTVkFYqW63F4fpR2pMrG.jpg","credit":"Image Credit: Hewlett-Packard","align":"","id":"JpCTVkFYqW63F4fpR2pMrG","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/JpCTVkFYqW63F4fpR2pMrG.jpg","alt":""},"id":"b0a95ea7-ad46-431a-87d3-3d52c2b62492","type":"image"},{"data":{"attributes":{"data-widget-type":"bestof","data-model-name":"HP Stream"},"source":"hawk","embedtype":"unknown"},"id":"19538713-9ae9-49b0-bd06-56404130ca03","type":"embed"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["If you&#39;re looking for inexpensive school laptops, don&#39;t worry, they really do exist. The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/HP-Stream-11-y010nr-Celeron-Personal/dp/B01JLCKP48?ttr_best-laptops-for-college-students-20&amp;ascsubtag=TTRV-ttr:en_US_43_PicStory_20\">HP Stream</a>, for example, doesn&#39;t break $200. Even so, it comes with full access to Office 365 and 1TB of OneDrive storage for one year, so you can access necessary programs for school assignments. It also features a built-in webcam so you can use Skype or Google Hangouts to video call home. This is a very simple laptop, so there is no optical d