on.com/Dell-Inspiron-Touchscreen-Flagship-Computer/dp/B07FLSSYVR?tag=ttr_default-20&amp;ascsubtag=TTRV51321532726342229-ttr:en_US_43_PicStory_20\">Dell Premium FHD Inspiron</a>. It uses an Intel Core i5 Processor, solid state drive, offers two USB ports, HDMI port, headphone jack, and web camera. However, this particular laptop does not offer a DVD drive so you&#39;ll need to stream any entertainment you want to watch."]},"id":"e8526202-7678-49dd-8020-fc9a926aaab6","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Software-Heavy Laptops - Graphic Design, Architecture, Engineering"},"id":"81dc0329-5c11-4a12-8f8f-49e1d6b435e0","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/pNkkZUogVoQcGqY6LbJ7mD.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":false,"importSrc":"http://media.bestofmicro.com/0/N/786695/original/MacBook-Pro.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pNkkZUogVoQcGqY6LbJ7mD.jpg","credit":"Image Credit: Apple","align":"","id":"pNkkZUogVoQcGqY6LbJ7mD","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/pNkkZUogVoQcGqY6LbJ7mD.jpg","alt":""},"id":"67a52f8e-6c5a-44ac-86bb-dee29251da75","type":"image"},{"data":{"attributes":{"data-widget-type":"bestof","data-model-name":"MacBook Pro"},"source":"hawk","embedtype":"unknown"},"id":"9c5e262d-caac-4628-8a9f-4b2bb3a4e02b","type":"embed"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["If you&#39;re planning on working with the Adobe Creative Cloud towards a degree in design, odds are your classmates and professors will be using Apple computers. This means, it will likely be easier to use the software on a Mac since the hotkeys and button icons will be the same as what your teachers teach you. Some might claim that the Suite works better on Mac vs. PC, but really, it&#39;s just a matter of preference. The MacBook Pro is the laptop of choice for many designers. It comes in many different size and power options but if you’re wanting the cheapest option, you&#39;ll probably want the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Apple-MacBook-Quad-Core-Storage-MR9U2LL/dp